<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-Hant">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>語音轉文字工具｜Whisper Transcriber</title>
  <style>
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", "Noto Sans TC", Arial, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #07111f 0%, #0b1d35 48%, #07111f 100%);
      color: #ffffff;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    a {
      color: inherit;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .page {
      min-height: 100vh;
      overflow: hidden;
      position: relative;
    }

    .glow {
      position: absolute;
      width: 420px;
      height: 420px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: rgba(0, 183, 255, 0.28);
      filter: blur(90px);
      top: -120px;
      right: -120px;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .glow-2 {
      position: absolute;
      width: 360px;
      height: 360px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: rgba(43, 98, 255, 0.22);
      filter: blur(90px);
      bottom: 120px;
      left: -140px;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    header {
      width: min(1120px, calc(100% - 32px));
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 22px 0;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
    }

    .logo {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }

    .logo-icon {
      width: 36px;
      height: 36px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #23d5ff, #3967ff);
      box-shadow: 0 0 28px rgba(35, 213, 255, 0.45);
    }

    .nav-link {
      padding: 10px 16px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.16);
      border-radius: 999px;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.86);
      font-size: 14px;
      backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    }

    main {
      width: min(1120px, calc(100% - 32px));
      margin: 0 auto;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .hero {
      min-height: calc(100vh - 82px);
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.05fr 0.95fr;
      gap: 44px;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 36px 0 80px;
    }

    .badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      color: #06111f;
      background: #ffe23b;
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 8px 14px;
      font-weight: 900;
      transform: rotate(-2deg);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(255, 226, 59, 0.22);
      margin-bottom: 22px;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: clamp(42px, 7vw, 82px);
      line-height: 0.98;
      letter-spacing: -2.5px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    h1 span {
      color: #27d9ff;
      text-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(39, 217, 255, 0.35);
    }

    .subtitle {
      font-size: clamp(18px, 2.2vw, 23px);
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.82);
      max-width: 620px;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .cta-row {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 10px;
      min-height: 52px;
      padding: 0 22px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      font-weight: 800;
      transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #27d9ff, #3465ff);
      box-shadow: 0 18px 36px rgba(39, 132, 255, 0.36);
    }

    .btn-secondary {
      color: #ffffff;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.09);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.14);
    }

    .note {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.64);
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .features {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 14px;
      margin-top: 28px;
    }

    .feature {
      padding: 18px;
      border-radius: 22px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.075);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.11);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    }

    .feature strong {
      display: block;
      font-size: 18px;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .feature p {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65);
    }

    .phone-wrap {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      position: relative;
    }

    .phone {
      width: min(360px, 86vw);
      border-radius: 42px;
      background: #101827;
      padding: 14px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.22);
      box-shadow: 0 35px 90px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.48), 0 0 60px rgba(35, 213, 255, 0.18);
      transform: rotate(4deg);
    }

    .screen {
      min-height: 610px;
      border-radius: 32px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #ffffff 0%, #edf5ff 100%);
      color: #0b1220;
      padding: 26px 20px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .screen-title {
      font-weight: 900;
      font-size: 22px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .step {
      margin: 14px 0;
    }

    .step-label {
      color: #3465ff;
      font-weight: 900;
      font-size: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .input-box {
      background: #ffffff;
      border: 1px solid #dbe5f1;
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 14px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(11, 18, 32, 0.06);
    }

    .chips {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 8px;
    }

    .chip {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 10px 8px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      background: #f4f7fb;
      border: 1px solid #dbe5f1;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .chip.active {
      color: #ffffff;
      background: #3465ff;
      border-color: #3465ff;
    }

    .convert-btn {
      margin-top: 24px;
      width: 100%;
      border: 0;
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #27d9ff, #3465ff);
      color: #ffffff;
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 900;
      padding: 16px;
      box-shadow: 0 14px 28px rgba(52, 101, 255, 0.28);
    }

    .result-card {
      margin-top: 18px;
      padding: 16px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: #07111f;
      color: #ffffff;
    }

    .result-card small {
      color: #27d9ff;
      font-weight: 900;
    }

    .section {
      padding: 70px 0;
    }

    .section h2 {
      font-size: clamp(30px, 4vw, 48px);
      margin-bottom: 18px;
      letter-spacing: -1px;
    }

    .cards {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 18px;
      margin-top: 24px;
    }

    .card {
      padding: 24px;
      border-radius: 24px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.075);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
    }

    .card h3 {
      font-size: 22px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .card p {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.68);
      font-size: 15px;
    }

    footer {
      width: min(1120px, calc(100% - 32px));
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 40px 0 60px;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.58);
      font-size: 14px;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    }

    @media (max-width: 860px) {
      .hero {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 34px;
        padding-top: 24px;
      }

      .features,
      .cards {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .phone {
        transform: rotate(0deg);
      }

      .screen {
        min-height: 560px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="page">
    <div class="glow"></div>
    <div class="glow-2"></div>

    <header>
      <a class="logo" href="#">
        <span class="logo-icon">🎙️</span>
        <span>Whisper Transcriber</span>
      </a>
      <a class="nav-link" href="https://github.com/dw5000tw-33/whisper-transcriber" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub 下載</a>
    </header>

    <main>
      <section class="hero">
        <div>
          <div class="badge">免費使用・語音轉文字</div>
          <h1>錄音秒變<br><span>文字</span></h1>
          <p class="subtitle">
            支援錄音檔與網路串流音檔，選好模型與語言後，一鍵轉成文字。會議紀錄、影片字幕、訪談整理、海報文案都能更快完成。
          </p>

          <div class="cta-row">
            <a class="btn btn-primary" href="https://github.com/dw5000tw-33/whisper-transcriber" target="_blank" rel="noopener">下載工具</a>
            <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="#how">查看使用方式</a>
          </div>

          <p class="note">由珊珊整理製作，歡迎加入官方 Line 交流使用問題。</p>

          <div class="features">
            <div class="feature">
              <strong>支援音檔</strong>
              <p>錄音檔、影片音訊、網路音檔網址。</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
              <strong>多種模型</strong>
              <p>tiny、base、small、medium、large。</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
              <strong>多語言</strong>
              <p>支援中文、英文、日文、韓文與自動偵測。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="phone-wrap">
          <div class="phone">
            <div class="screen">
              <div class="screen-title">語音轉文字工具</div>

              <div class="step">
                <div class="step-label">1 選擇音檔</div>
                <div class="input-box">
                  <span>錄音檔.m4a</span>
                  <span>✅</span>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="step">
                <div class="step-label">2 選擇模型</div>
                <div class="chips">
                  <div class="chip">tiny</div>
                  <div class="chip">base</div>
                  <div class="chip active">small</div>
                  <div class="chip">medium</div>
                  <div class="chip">large</div>
                  <div class="chip">auto</div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="step">
                <div class="step-label">3 選擇語言</div>
                <div class="input-box">
                  <span>自動偵測</span>
                  <span>⌄</span>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="step">
                <div class="step-label">4 輸出位置</div>
                <div class="input-box">
                  <span>C:/Users/Output</span>
                  <span>📁</span>
                </div>
              </div>

              <button class="convert-btn">開始轉檔</button>

              <div class="result-card">
                <small>完成</small>
                <p>文字已輸出，可直接丟給 AI 做摘要、字幕、簡報或海報文案。</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section" id="how">
        <h2>怎麼使用？</h2>
        <div class="cards">
          <div class="card">
            <h3>1. 開啟程式</h3>
            <p>下載專案後執行 Python 程式，打開本機操作頁面。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <h3>2. 選擇音檔</h3>
            <p>選擇本機錄音檔，或貼上網路音檔網址，再設定輸出位置。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <h3>3. 一鍵轉文字</h3>
            <p>依照音檔狀況選擇模型，按下轉檔，等待完成即可。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section">
        <h2>適合誰使用？</h2>
        <div class="cards">
          <div class="card">
            <h3>做短影音</h3>
            <p>快速把錄音變成字幕稿，剪片更省時間。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <h3>會議紀錄</h3>
            <p>把會議錄音轉成文字，再交給 AI 摘要重點。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <h3>內容創作者</h3>
            <p>訪談、教學、講稿、Podcast 都能更快整理。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
      <p>Whisper Transcriber｜免費語音轉文字工具</p>
      <p>下載連結：https://github.com/dw5000tw-33/whisper-transcriber</p>
    </footer>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
